00:01:22,780 --> 00:01:24,730
'To emerge victorious in this war,

2
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:27,790
we must devise a stratagem to take down

3
00:01:27,900 --> 00:01:28,980
His Majesty Bhisma.'

4
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,560
'On the day of the war.'

5
00:04:52,620 --> 00:04:54,360
Madhav!

6
00:04:54,450 --> 00:04:56,620
Your chariot's here, Parth.

7
00:04:57,620 --> 00:05:00,560
Along with the charioteer.

8
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,590
No, Madhav.

9
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:08,330
You can't become my charioteer.

10
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,520
Do you not believe me, Parth?

11
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:14,290
I am very proficient with this.

12
00:05:14,380 --> 00:05:15,450
No, Madhav.

13
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:17,460
You are a respected person.

14
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:21,290
I can't let you become a charioteer.

15
00:05:21,420 --> 00:05:24,450
It doesn't matter, Parth.

16
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:27,430
If you feel like it

17
00:05:28,350 --> 00:05:29,490
then consider me

18
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:32,320
just sitting in front of you.

19
00:05:35,550 --> 00:05:38,430
As the horses are in my care

20
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:43,330
I'll never let your mind waver, Parth.

21
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:46,360
In honesty and deception...

22
00:05:46,550 --> 00:05:48,530
Between truth and immorality...

23
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:53,460
Every time your mind
loses focus

24
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:57,520
it would be my duty

25
00:05:58,550 --> 00:06:01,430
to bring you to the 
right course again.

26
00:06:03,420 --> 00:06:05,330
Both in custody of your chariot

27
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:07,420
or your life,

28
00:06:11,250 --> 00:06:13,390
I am proficient in both, Parth.

29
00:07:20,250 --> 00:07:24,220
All hail Mahadev!

30
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:27,230
All hail Mahadev!

31
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,190
Karna.

32
00:08:20,250 --> 00:08:23,130
I will wait for you
on the battlefield.

33
00:08:23,350 --> 00:08:26,130
Until you draw your bowstring

34
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:29,120
we will not achieve victory.

35
00:08:30,250 --> 00:08:33,130
I also wait for that day, 
friend.

36
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:37,230
I may be physically here

37
00:08:38,250 --> 00:08:39,390
but my soul

38
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:43,130
will accompany you in the battlefield.

39
00:10:31,050 --> 00:10:35,020
All hail Mahadev!
- All hail Mahadev!

