00:10:37,020 --> 00:10:40,960
All hail Mahadev!
- All hail Mahadev!

41
00:10:45,250 --> 00:10:47,200
May God bless you
with victory, sons.

42
00:10:48,250 --> 00:10:52,130
May your war skills
will make you immortal.

43
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,960
I bless you all.

44
00:11:07,980 --> 00:11:09,960
Do not worry about me, mother.

45
00:11:18,250 --> 00:11:19,990
Sire!

46
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:22,030
I assure you that this day

47
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:24,190
I'll be back with victory
from the battlefield.

48
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,080
Dear...

49
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:55,090
I hope you win.

50
00:11:56,020 --> 00:11:59,050
Your victory in this war is decided.

51
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:09,000
Accept my last greeting, mother.

52
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,920
No one realizes

53
00:12:15,950 --> 00:12:17,120
that at the end of this war

54
00:12:17,950 --> 00:12:20,020
who will greet the god of death,

55
00:12:22,180 --> 00:12:25,930
and who will go through life

56
00:12:26,180 --> 00:12:28,060
with memories of the war.

57
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:33,020
People of Kuru along with the Arya clan

58
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:37,060
including women, children,
pottery, blacksmith,

59
00:12:37,050 --> 00:12:38,050
and farmers.

60
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:41,100
All will survive, my son.

61
00:12:42,150 --> 00:12:44,960
to have pleasures in life.

62
00:12:46,150 --> 00:12:50,100
Your enemy is also
enemy to society.

63
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,960
Have no mercy on them.

64
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:02,860
Fill the vessel of god Bhairav* with blood, my child.
