00:13:19,830 --> 00:13:23,680
All hail Mahadev!
- All hail Mahadev!

67
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:33,600
Order the attack,
brother Yudhishtir.

68
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:42,570
Charioteer,

69
00:15:42,660 --> 00:15:43,730
take the chariot to the front.

70
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:12,960
Yudhishtir.
Are you already scared?

71
00:18:15,860 --> 00:18:19,000
Repent for your actions and 
accept your punishment,

72
00:18:20,820 --> 00:18:21,930
Dusshasan,

73
00:18:22,820 --> 00:18:26,740
time to ask forgiveness 
has long gone.

74
00:18:28,820 --> 00:18:33,000
But if you want to save
your soldiers' life

75
00:18:34,860 --> 00:18:36,800
then surrender yourself

76
00:18:37,760 --> 00:18:41,900
and accept the death penalty,
brother Yudhishtir.

77
00:18:48,890 --> 00:18:52,800
At least your righteousness will 
live longer than you.

78
00:18:57,960 --> 00:18:59,800
Grandsire Bhishma!

79
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:01,860
Do not forget

80
00:19:03,760 --> 00:19:07,730
that you had taken oath

81
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:08,930
for the throne of Hastinapur.

82
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:15,800
Uncle speaks right, grandsire.

83
00:19:16,990 --> 00:19:19,940
Do not bless me.

84
00:19:22,820 --> 00:19:24,960
But before this war begins

85
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:28,790
I will not give up my ethic.

86
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:33,890
Therefore, by greeting you

87
00:19:34,760 --> 00:19:36,890
and our teacher...

88
00:19:39,790 --> 00:19:41,700
me and my brothers

89
00:19:42,720 --> 00:19:44,790
here to ask for your permissions
for war,

90
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:33,760
Grandsire,

91
00:20:34,860 --> 00:20:37,670
like birds build their nests

92
00:20:37,820 --> 00:20:41,700
on branches in the shade of trees
and live happily

93
00:20:42,790 --> 00:20:45,670
we've been living in a safe place 
because of you.

94
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:49,670
Every part of us is indebted 
to you.

95
00:20:56,890 --> 00:20:58,630
Today...

96
00:21:02,720 --> 00:21:05,900
we have been forced to take up 
arms against you.

97
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:13,700
Like aquatic animals trying to 
drink up dry the entire ocean.

98
00:21:13,890 --> 00:21:17,700
Grandsire,

99
00:21:22,760 --> 00:21:24,790
give us permission to war,

100
00:21:25,860 --> 00:21:29,630
or order us to surrender
our weapons.

